ZH: 1. 他一直渴望独立自主，不愿受到他人的控制。
EN: 1. He has always longed for independence and autonomy, unwilling to be controlled by others.

ZH: 2. 总统宣布国家将会保持独立自主的立场。
EN: 2. The president declared that the country will maintain its independent and autonomous position.

ZH: 3. 这个部门享有独立自主的权利，可以自行做出决策。
EN: 3. This department has the right to be independent and autonomous, able to make decisions on its own.

ZH: 4. 作为独立自主的个体，她总是有着自己独立思考的能力。
EN: 4. As an independent and autonomous individual, she always has the ability to think for herself.

ZH: 5. 他们的公司一直被视为是一个独立自主的企业。
EN: 5. Their company has always been seen as an independent and autonomous enterprise.

ZH: 6. 这个团体坚持独立自主地进行活动，不受外界的影响。
EN: 6. This group insists on operating independently and autonomously, not influenced by external factors.

ZH: 7. 她选择了一个独立自主的生活方式，没有依赖他人。
EN: 7. She chose an independent and autonomous lifestyle, without relying on others.

ZH: 8. 这些组织工作以独立自主之名，为公民提供服务。
EN: 8. These organizations work under the name of independence and autonomy, providing services for citizens.

ZH: 9. 那个国家一直坚持独立自主，不受其他国家的影响。
EN: 9. That country has always maintained independence and autonomy, not influenced by other nations.

ZH: 10. 这位领导者强调人们应该有独立自主的思维和行动能力。
EN: 10. The leader emphasized that people should have independent and autonomous thinking and action capabilities.

ZH: 11. 公司支持员工在工作中展现独立自主的态度。
EN: 11. The company supports employees in showing an independent and autonomous attitude at work.

ZH: 12. 她喜欢独立自主地进行工作，不喜欢被人指挥。
EN: 12. She enjoys working independently and autonomously, not liking to be ordered around.

ZH: 13. 这个组织致力于为残疾人提供独立自主的生活环境。
EN: 13. This organization is committed to providing a living environment that promotes independence and autonomy for people with disabilities.

ZH: 14. 这个项目的目标是培养学生独立自主地思考和解决问题。
EN: 14. The goal of this project is to cultivate students to think and solve problems independently and autonomously.

ZH: 15. 那个小岛宣布独立自主，脱离了母国的统治。
EN: 15. The island declared independence and autonomy, breaking away from the rule of the mother country.

ZH: 16. 成年人应该拥有自主独立的权利，可以自己做决定。
EN: 16. Adults should have the right to independent and autonomous decision-making.

ZH: 17. 这家企业一直以独立自主的形象示人，享有良好声誉。
EN: 17. This company has always presented itself as independent and autonomous, enjoying a good reputation.

ZH: 18. 我们应该鼓励孩子独立自主地做事，培养他们的能力。
EN: 18. We should encourage children to do things independently and autonomously, cultivating their ability.

ZH: 19. 每个人都应该有独立自主的思想和行动意识。
EN: 19. Everyone should have independent and autonomous thinking and action awareness.

ZH: 20. 这个社区提倡独立自主的精神，并尊重每个人的选择。
EN: 20. This community advocates the spirit of independence and autonomy, respecting the choices of each individual.
